==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Montre
<hw>Mon"tre</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., show, show case,
organ case.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Organ Building)</fld> <def>A stop,
usually the open diapason, having its pipes ⟦ldquo⟧shown⟦rdquo⟧ as part
of the organ case, or otherwise specially mounted.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A hole in the wall of a pottery kiln, by which the
state of the pieces within can be judged.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Montross</ent>⟦br⟧
